metadata.name: Jeweled Falcon #1
metadata.description: Jeweled Falcon Club – created by Forevercorp Digital – is designed for lovers of luxury bling. Each high utility Jeweled Falcon NFT is proof of membership of the club which provides privileges to members including exclusive access to a metaverse space to be developed as an atelier showcasing diamonds, luxury jewelry and watches, gemstones and NFTs; priority access to the future token offers of Forevercorp; & discounted offers of gemstones and merchandise. And for holders of 10 or more NFTs there are annual distributions of loyalty rewards from the sponsorship from the Forevercorp group of companies.
